description: This repository contains various XXE labs set up for different languages and their different parsers. This may alternatively serve as a playground to teach or test with Vulnerability scanners / WAF rules / Secure Configuration settings.

Social Media Website with SPA (Single Page Application) Frontend made with Angular, TypeScript and REST server with Express.js and MongoDB, it consist of Guest part for unauthenticated users and User part for authenticated users. The authentication is made with JWT (JSON Web Token). Both made by me
My information security blog

EDUCATIONAL PURPOSES ONLY: Proof of concept for memory leak ransomware. This software will add itself to local startup creating a 1MB memory leak until password P@thf1nder&quot; is entered. Removal requires deleting 'BlueComet' from registry.
